Sphere: Protection Sphere<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage cast dust devil<br/><br/>
<br/>
This spell will summon a dust devil to guard you.  The dust devil can be<br/>
controlled by telling it what you want it to do.  For example, typing<br/>
'tell dust devil shout Hello' would cause the dust devil to shout 'Hello'.<br/>
